    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Textile with linen warp and woolen weft, usually homespun and handwoven, and later also with a cotton warp.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
